  "content": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Clinical Setting"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Specific therapy for Legionella endocarditis in patient with prosthetic valve.",
        "Culture-negative prosthetic valve endocarditis; often nosocomial.",
        "Diagnosis by isolation of the organism from resected valve tissue but with special handling may also be isolated from blood culture."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Etiologies"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Legionella spp."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Primary Regimens"
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Levofloxacin",
            "dose": "750 mg",
            "route": "po/IV",
            "frequency": "once daily"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Azithromycin",
            "dose": "500 mg",
            "route": "po/IV",
            "frequency": "once daily"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Alternative Regimens"
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Doxycycline",
            "dose": "200 mg",
            "route": "po/IV",
            "frequency": "bid"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Erythromycin",
            "dose": "500 mg",
            "route": "po/IV",
            "frequency": "q6h",
            "connector": "+"
          },
          {
            "drug": "Rifampin",
            "dose": "600-1200 mg",
            "route": "po",
            "notes": "in 2 or more divided doses"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Ciprofloxacin",
            "dose": "400 mg",
            "route": "IV",
            "frequency": "q12h",
            "connector": "or"
          },
          {
            "drug": "Ciprofloxacin",
            "dose": "500 mg",
            "route": "po",
            "frequency": "bid"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Combination of erythromycin and ciprofloxacin has also been used (Emerg Infect Dis 18:95, 2012)."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Antimicrobial Stewardship"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Advise microbiology laboratory when considering the diagnosis of Legionella spp. endocarditis as it is possible to isolate the organism in blood culture media with special handling.",
        "Duration of therapy unknown, most patients have been treated for at least 5 months.",
        "Infectious Diseases consultation recommended"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Comments"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Several Legionella spp have been reported as causes of endocarditis.",
        "Most patients reported in the literature have undergone valve replacement in addition to medical therapy.",
        "Treatment recommendations based on anecdotal case reports.",
        "References: J Infect 51:e256, 2005, Clin Micro Rev 14:177, 2001, Circulation. 2015;132:1435-1486."
      ]
    }
  ]
}